These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-1::.
There 2 different types of food: cranberry, zucchini
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: badminton, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is badminton is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is not the person eating zucchini##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | zucchini   | cranberry  |
| Sport   | badminton | weightlifting |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-2::.
There 2 different types of food: radish, asparagus
2 different pets are kept: hedgehog, pony
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is not the person eating asparagus##6

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1   |     2      |
| Food   | radish | asparagus      |
| Pet    | hedgehog  | pony |

 #################################

 
