.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-5::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: thriller, western
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: basketball, rugby
1. the person watching western movies is not the person who's sport is rugby##6
2. the person watching western movies is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is rugby##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller  | western |
| Sport         | rugby | basketball      |

