.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-7::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  chef, journalist
2 different pets are kept: bird, horse
1. the chef is in an odd position##4
2. the chef is not the owner of the horse##6

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1      |       2       |
| Job   | chef | journalist |
| Pet   | bird       | horse       |

